==== UI
==================================================
  
I am traveling and can bring stuff along for others.

  ==> Where do you depart from? (Airport code / Country - Province/State - City)

(get from http://www.maxmind.com/app/worldcities)

 Select Country (doable)
 Load / Select State (sub-country region)
 Select City

  ==> Where are you traveling to? (one or more destinations) 

 Select Country (doable)
 Load / Select State (sub-country region)
 Select City [Add]

Selecting a country loads state (if state available in Db)
Selecting a state loads cities
Selecting a city and clicking add adds the city into a list.

[AQUI VOY]

I want someone to bring something for me.



AntTrade

A website to:

Have people request travelers to bring them stuff from their places of origin.

UI:

For people who need stuff, a way to express the need:

   From (country - city - region), please bring me (this and that).

   I will pay the value of the merchandise (in Euro) and also (X euro/USD/etc) comission for bringing it.

   (an expiry date)

Also, to contact travelers who have stated they're going somewhere and ask them to bring something for them.


For travelers:

A form to enter where they're departing from and where they're going to, to state that they're available to bring something along.

Also, search for recipients in the city they're going to, and offer to bring their stuff to them.


