Main page:

1. Create hello world template.

Hello world

2. Create translation page (in English) to translated hello world page. (Translate page, selectors for language, and template name. Shows all tags in the template + English version.)

3. Create user, inserts user in users table, sends verification email, sends user to landing "home" page.

4. Add user rights. User, admin, translator. Only allow admins and translators to see the translate page.

5. Develop the application.












